title: 1849 P Liberty Gold Piece $20 American Mint State
description: 1849 p liberty gold piece 20 american mint state it is an indescribable experience to handle the huge 20 double eagle tribute in todays world of clad circulating coinage and plastic credit cards its difficult to imagine the original splendid heavy pieces were once actually used as money americas largest circulating gold coin the double eagle was born during the rousing years of the great california gold rush the enormous masses of gold hauled out of the hills by the 49ers helped fuel the growth of the american west and dramatically changed the nations gold coinage the first shipment of california gold to the philadelphia mint weighed just over 230 ounces and most of this was coined into small denomination quarter eagles record amounts of gold rolled steadily into the mint and it was logical to convert as much of it as possible into coins preferably without having to increase the mints existing facilities one obvious solution was to create a much larger denomination than the currently authorized quarter half and eagle pieces the introduction of the new 20 double eagle meant twice the coinage value of the existing 10 gold eagle could be produced using the same equipment and facilities the design of the new coin fell to chief engraver james b longacre who used a similar motif for two new denominations the gold dollar and the 20 gold piece lady liberty appearing on the obverse wears a pearlbordered diadem with the inscription liberty the crouching venus an ancient grecoroman sculpture served as the inspiration for the distinguished portrait the reverse is based on the great seal of the united states the double eagle or 20 gold piece is the largest denomination of all circulating coins ever issued by the u s mint james longacre designed a grecoroman portrait of liberty wearing a coronet inscribed with liberty this is a restrike not original the great seal of the united states appears on the reverseto honor the landmark gold coin this collectors proof is minted under the strictest quality standards and struck multiple times for razor sharp design details and a brilliant finishcoin is composed of brass and layered with 24kt gold it is a nontradable replica cointribute of the worlds most rare and beautiful coinssouvenir collectible for a coin collectionthe double eagle or 20 gold piece is the largest denomination of all circulating coins ever issued by the u s mint
